<h1>Search</h1>

<h3>Combine</h3>
<p>AND, OR, NOT. Example: <i>art* OR kunst*</i>
    <br>The operators must be written in capital letters, default is AND.
</p>

<h3>Phrase search, using quotation marks</h3>
<p><i>"street art"</i> = the words must be adjacent
    <br><i>"street art"~5</i> = must be present within 5 words
    <br><br>Also use quotation marks for:
    <br>- ISBN, ISSN
    <br>- hyphenated words
</p>



